## Migrate to Firebolt

Firebolt supports seamless migration from other data platforms, helping you modernize your analytics workloads with faster performance, flexible scaling, and efficient resource management.  

This section provides step-by-step guidance on migrating from supported platforms to Firebolt. Learn how to adjust your architecture, redesign your schema, and translate queries to take advantage of Fireboltâ€™s engine-based model, indexing, and advanced query optimization.  

